[rev_slider alias="home-default"][/rev_slider]

Imagine A Theme So Easily Customizable

You Will Be Able to Adjust It in Just 5 Mins!

Designed with true multipurposeness in mind, this theme makes a case for how minimalistic and yet fully functional a WordPress-based template might be, if done right.
Powerful Options
Powered by a diverse multitude of plugins and layouts, Bryte provides you with a highly functional web business tools...
Power Builder
Whether it’s a minor tweak or a major reshuffle you want to apply, Power Builder makes editing so much easier and faster!
Responsive Layout
In the world of today, people come across a website via screens of all sizes. Bryte is optimized for tablets, phones & desktops.
24/7 Support
Known for working around just about any issues, our tech support will always be glad to help you online, on a 24/7 basis!
WOOcommerce Compatible
Ecommerce grows so fast it seems impossible to ignore Bryte will allow that, being e-store friendly and Woocmmerce compatible.
Pro to Its Core
Developed by a team known for quality, Bryte has a range of designs, plugins, editing options and everything else you might need!

Theme So Flexible and Adaptive,

That It WIll Fit Any Business in Any Niche!

While neutral themes have become somewhat mainstream lately, the holistic nature of Bryte makes it stand out from the rest…

What Makes This Theme Stand

Out Is an Extensive Range of Built-in Design Skins & Plugins!

8 Design Variations & 20+ Plugins
Versatile Aesthetics
When we were choosing a slate of design looks to go with, we’ve decided to make it as diverse and visually appealing as possible...
Full-on Functionality
Bryte’s featuring over 2 dozens of multifunctional plugins that are altogether meant to drastically enhance your website’s performance. Blog Layouts and Even WooCommerce Compatibility!

Sometimes a website needs more than just a streamlined design and a few page types. The Brythe theme indeed has more - layout, design and functionality-wise! More info
What People Say?

Testimonials

When I was tasked with choosing a new theme for our company website, the choice was obvious - Bryte had everything we needed.
John Burgundy Developer
Being a freelance designer, I pay a lot of attention to the aesthetics of a theme. Luckily, the Bryte theme has the looks I want!
Walter Walkate Developer
As an owner of a small business I rely heavily on people discovering me online. This was the reason I chose this theme!
Jessica Potocky Developer

In Partnership

This is a List of Partners

Needless to say that we here feel very strongly about working in partnership with other developers, ideas and technologies.

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Bryte Boasts Clean and Crispy Design,

Bulletproof Layout Consistency and Intuitive Navigation.

The theme was created by top industry leaders in web design and user experience. Improve your audience engagement and loyalty with simple and user friendly tools offered by our theme.

Who We Are

United team of like-minded people ready to offer the best services!

Being helpful and meet your needs on short notice is our motto and lifestyle.
Versatile Aesthetics
When we were choosing a slate of design looks to go with, we’ve decided to make it as diverse and visually appealing as possible...
Full-on Functionality
Bryte’s featuring over 2 dozens of multifunctional plugins that are altogether meant to drastically enhance your website’s performance.
Versatile Aesthetics
When we were choosing a slate of design looks to go with, we’ve decided to make it as diverse and visually appealing as possible...
Full-on Functionality
Bryte’s featuring over 2 dozens of multifunctional plugins that are altogether meant to drastically enhance your website’s performance.

In Partnership

This is a List of Partners

Needless to say that we here feel very strongly about working in partnership with other developers, ideas and technologies.

We Got the Skills

We Have it All, and a Bit More for Luck.

Needless to say that we here feel very strongly about working in partnership with other developers, ideas and technologies.
Powerful Options
Powered by a diverse multitude of plugins and layouts, Bryte provides you with a highly functional web business tools...
Power Builder
Whether it’s a minor tweak or a major reshuffle you want to apply, Power Builder makes editing so much easier and faster!
Responsive Layout
In the world of today, people come across a website via screens of all sizes. Bryte is optimized for tablets, phones & desktops.
24/7 Support
Known for working around just about any issues, our tech support will always be glad to help you online, on a 24/7 basis!
WOOcommerce Compatible
Ecommerce grows so fast it seems impossible to ignore Bryte will allow that, being e-store friendly and Woocmmerce compatible.
Pro to Its Core
Developed by a team known for quality, Bryte has a range of designs, plugins, editing options and everything else you might need!

Bryte Offers You More, Including Custom Headers,

Blog Layouts and Even WooCommerce Compatibility!

Sometimes a website needs more than just a streamlined design and a few page types. The Brythe theme indeed has more - layout, design and functionality-wise! Perfect

Solution

for Both Desktop and Mobile Projects
Learn more

Main Theme Advantages are

Pixel Perfect Design & Clear Code Delivered Right to You

The theme has clean code and pixel-perfect design, created with the thought of the most important customer needs.
Powerful Options
Powered by a diverse multitude of plugins and layouts, Bryte provides you with a highly functional web business tools...
Power Builder
Whether it’s a minor tweak or a major reshuffle you want to apply, Power Builder makes editing so much easier and faster!

Attractive on the Outside.

Effective on the Inside

In this theme innovative development meets with creative approach to the implementation of effective design. Grasp the best of it with a brand new multipurpose theme!

Experience what a Really Fast

Installation Is With Cherry Wizard Plugin

From now on you’ll be able to install the theme within minutes with all the plugins and demo content included. Fastest Theme Installation Cherry Wizard will install the theme automatically, so you won’t have to worry about common installation problems! One-Click Plugins Installation The plugin will provide you with the full list of necessary and recommended plugins, upload them and install them to the theme in one click! Smart Demo Content Installation No more messing up with .xml files! Cherry Wizard will add the necessary demo content to your website smoothly and easily!

More About Us

item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Each business niche may require a unique functionality of its own. With that notion in mind, our team of professional WordPress coders has been working day and night to roll out a definitive collection of built-in WordPress plugins, that come with each of our WordPress themes… Due to the fact that this is a WordPress theme, the process of installing it and using it is truly as easy as it gets! Read our documentation to understand how fast you can go from purchasing a JetImpex WordPress theme to actually using it as a live skin for your company’s webpage. Also, the WordPress CMS (Content Management System) allows you to easily change the content (text; multimedia; blocks; pages) of any part of your new theme!
In the modern days of a very tight online business competition, ranking high in such search engines as Google, Bing or Yahoo is critical. With the help of our heavy customizations, each of our Business WordPress Themes is enhanced with an optimized features. Believe us, Google will just love crawling your new website! All in all, feel free to browse our Business WordPress Themes category and you will definitely find a new look for your company’s website!

item.content:encoded: When you need your company to have a new website or if you venture on updating your old webpage with a new look and functionality, the choices are versatile. Assuming that you will go the easy way and choose a theme for your WordPress website, the overall number of characteristics that you will need to keep in mind narrows down significantly. But how do you stay focused on what kind of a template you need and what do you want to get from that template? We recommend focusing on 4 most essential characteristics, each vital for your company’s to have an efficient and long-standing online presence! All the WordPress themes that we have here have had a vast team of professional designers sketching, working and executing the ultimate visual look for it. With such a wide range of choices at hand, we strongly advise you to stick to the WordPress Theme that is based on your business’ or a closely related field. Either way, thanks to all the diversity here you will be able to choose a Theme that can be either of a formal color scheme with some light colors in it or a more vivid one, featuring bold textures and hues!

item.title: About Me
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
I am experienced illustrator

and web designer keen on travelling

Sharing my ideas and impressions with people inspires me for creating new projects! I always was interested in extreme sports and tourism. I adore visiting unusual places, wild abandoned places as well as enjoying the beauty of the ocean and nature. I can’t imagine my life without illustration and design and never stop developing my skills and getting new knowledge. I hope my works can help you with your business and needs. I’m always ready for dialogue and I find it awesome to discuss the ideas with you. Powerful Theme Options 55% Powerful Theme Options 55% Powerful Theme Options 55%

item.title: About Me & My Work
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
About Me & My Work

and web designer keen on travelling

The theme was created by top industry leaders in web design and user experience. I always was interested in extreme sports and tourism. I adore visiting unusual places, wild abandoned places as well as enjoying the beauty of the ocean and nature. I can’t imagine my life without illustration and design and never stop developing my skills and getting new knowledge. I hope my works can help you with your business and needs. I’m always ready for dialogue and I find it awesome to discuss the ideas with you. You can see my works in the Gallery page or at my Instagram account. I’m a very responsible in working with clients and try to meet all the demands. I understand that my point of view can differ from yours, but it’s pleasure  for me to create a perfect product that you like.

item.title: Using Woocommerce Right
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
When you need your company to have a new website or if you venture on updating your old webpage with a new look and functionality, the choices are versatile. Assuming that you will go the easy way and choose a theme for your WordPress website, the overall number of characteristics that you will need to keep in mind narrows down significantly. But how do you stay focused on what kind of a template you need and what do you want to get from that template? We recommend focusing on 4 most essential characteristics, each vital for your company’s to have an efficient and long-standing online presence! All the WordPress themes that we have here have had a vast team of professional designers sketching, working and executing the ultimate visual look for it. With such a wide range of choices at hand, we strongly advise you to stick to the WordPress Theme that is based on your business’ or a closely related field. Either way, thanks to all the diversity here you will be able to choose a Theme that can be either of a formal color scheme with some light colors in it or a more vivid one, featuring bold textures and hues!
It’s perfect to display the members of your staff, team or working force. Within Bryte theme you. Adam Smith
Each business niche may require a unique functionality of its own. With that notion in mind, our team of professional WordPress coders has been working day and night to roll out a definitive collection of built-in WordPress plugins, that come with each of our WordPress themes… Due to the fact that this is a WordPress theme, the process of installing it and using it is truly as easy as it gets! Read our documentation to understand how fast you can go from purchasing a JetImpex WordPress theme to actually using it as a live skin for your company’s webpage. Also, the WordPress CMS (Content Management System) allows you to easily change the content (text; multimedia; blocks; pages) of any part of your new theme! In the modern days of a very tight online business competition, ranking high in such search engines as Google, Bing or Yahoo is critical. With the help of our heavy customizations, each of our Business WordPress Themes is enhanced with an optimized features. Believe us, Google will just love crawling your new website! All in all, feel free to browse our Business WordPress Themes category and you will definitely find a new look for your company’s website!
